name: Hic et Nunc Creator Manifesto
description:
True words by N-LITE (Diskette Park), faux chiseled stone by Raw & Roll (Zugzwang).

Quote: "What they think I'm doing: making some techbros rich with a Ponzi scheme while trashing the planet. What I'm actually doing: finally making a living with my art on an ecologically sustainable platform and feeling like a part of a community for once in my life."

Originally released as HeN OBJKT 65594 on 05 May 2021.
